attributes.title: Regulation Gameplay // Geoff and Andrew F*ck Around in Warzone
attributes.description: With the goal of creating the greatest trailer of all time, Andrew and Geoff drop into Warzone to get some on the ground footage.  What is the trailer for?  Who knows!

attributes.title: Let's ask Eric and Andrew // Regulation Questions
attributes.description: To kick off the new year, Eric and Andrew sit down to play Halo and answer regulation questions from the community.

attributes.title: Regulation Gameplay // Fall Guys Stick Challenge Part 1
attributes.description: To test their gaming skills, Gavin has printed out a series of elongated thumb sticks for him and Andrew to equip for every Fall Guys win.

attributes.title: Regulation Gameplay // Cricket 22
attributes.description: It's the match of the ages as Gavin and Andrew face off in a blood-pumping game of Cricket.

attributes.title: The FINAL Frogger Achievement HAUNTED // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: This ACHIEVEMENT has HAUNTED Andrew for years now and with Geoff's help, he hopes to cross to the other side of his final Frogger achievement.

attributes.title: Ranked Duos in Rocket League // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: While being coached by Geoff and Gavin, Andrew and Nick attempt to get ranked in Rocket League duos while playing together for the first time.

attributes.title: Andrew Does MAGIC in Halo 2
attributes.description: Performing in front of his two man audience of Geoff and Gavin, Andrew performs a few classic "magic" tricks in Halo 2.

attributes.title: Gun Game in Call of Duty: Modern Warfare 3 // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description:
Thank you Activision for providing the codes for this video. 
 Gavin and Andrew set their boots on the ground to take on Spawn, Critter Man, and a tank that they may or may not be meant to shoot.

attributes.title: Trying NOT to Place Bronze in Halo Ranked // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Joined by Eric, Gavin and Andrew take on Halo Infinite Ranked to get their placement and see how they stack up against each other.

attributes.title: Geoff, Gavin, and Andrew Try to Get a Warzone Win // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Joined by special operative Gavin (Prince Harry), Andrew (Snoop Dogg), and Geoff (Character from Destiny) set out to get a trios win in Call of Duty Warzone.

attributes.title: Rewulation Gameplay // Wheel of Fortune Part 3
attributes.description: Wow, who knew you could spell box with the letter W. Gavin, Andrew, and Nick are invited to spin the wheel for a shot at winning it big!

attributes.title: We < 3 Mud // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Geoff (Giggle Bones), Gavin (Free Bird), Nick (Muddy Buddy), and Andrew get back in their big rigs and take on mud, rocks, and trees in Snowrunner.

attributes.title: Talking In Gavin's Secret Spot in Halo 2 // Regulation Talking
attributes.description: To test a theory from Gavin, Andrew and Geoff take to the metaphorical ""under the bleachers"" of Halo 2 lockout to see if this map has the ability to spark a magical conversation.

attributes.title: Small Soldiers Gameplay // Regulation Blindside
attributes.description: While many may have expected a Sopranos themed gameplay, Andrew hits Geoff, Gavin, Eric, and Nick with a Small Soldiers Blindside.

attributes.title: Halo Doubles in The Pit // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: No teammates are needed for Andrew and Gavin as they take on ranked doubles in Halo Infinite.

attributes.title: Trying To Redeem Ourselves in Halo Ranked // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Gavin and Andrew dive back into the grueling world of Halo Infinite Ranked to see if they can move their placements up, and definitely not drop to Bronze.

attributes.title: Shrapnel Filled Sh*t Show // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Looking to cause chaos and destruction; Andrew, Nick, and Gavin take on The Finals and are surprised by a special guest while in the heat of battle.

attributes.title: The Big ol' Bowl Simulation // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Instead of watching the other "big game" on Sunday you can join Geoff, Gavin, Eric, Andrew, Nick, and Graysie as they watch the definitive Madden 24 simulation to find the true winner of this years Big ol' Bowl.

attributes.title: How many times can we go BANKRUPT?! // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Our boys are back with even more wheel spinning! It would be a shame if someone went bankrupt and lost all of their money.

attributes.title: WE Suck at Parking // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Geoff, Gavin, Nick, and Andrew buckle up to decide who sucks at parking the most in You Suck At Parking.

attributes.title: My Stick Just KEEPS GETTING LONGER? // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Aiming to increase their stick length, Gavin and Andrew return to Fall Guys to secure some stick altering wins.

attributes.title: It's Been TEN YEARS...Where the Hell Are We? // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Andrew and Gavin hop into DayZ to start a new life together in the zombie apocalypse. Now they just gotta find each other.

attributes.title: We May Be The WORST Worms Players // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: It's Worms 3! Geoff, Gavin, Andrew, and Eric battle it out in another round of Worms where we see how much they've improved (or gotten worse?) between games.

attributes.title: Palworld Is Our Favorite Pokemon Game // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: In an attempt to be the very best; Andrew, Gavin, Geoff and Nick befriend some pals and make some enemies in Palworld.

attributes.title: This Game Caused SO MUCH DRAMA // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Geoff, Gavin, Andrew, and Eric are here with Worms. We've got it all: the destruction, the mistakes, the drama, the ultimate prize of sweet, sweet victory. What more could you possibly want?

attributes.title: Pipe Dreams Become Pipe Realities // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Geoff, Gavin, Andrew, and Nick are back in their trucks (along with Eric) and they're trying to complete a mission that they've been working on for awhile. Surely they're gonna be patient, throw that gear in to Low and not try to take shortcuts.

attributes.title: The Truck Boys Get A FIRST LOOK at Expeditions: A Mudrunner Game (EARLY ACCESS)
attributes.description:
Thanks to Saber Interactive and Focus Entertainment for early access to this game!
Geoff and the well known Truck Boys are here with a sneak peek at the new Expeditions: A Mudrunner Game! 
As one could imagine, Geoff and the Truck Boys are beyond ecstatic and thrilled to be playing this and showcasing the game for you all!

attributes.title: How Do Parachutes Work Again?! // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Geoff, Andrew, Nick, Gavin, and our extra special commentary squad member Eric, Try their hands at Warzone again! This time, they try to get some bomb drone kills against some unsuspecting paratroopers.

attributes.title: Who Wants to be a Millionaire? // March Mental Madness Part 1
attributes.description: Every Wednesday in the month of March, we'll be releasing an episode of March Mental Madness.  With host Andrew, contestants Geoff, Gavin, Nick, Graysie, and Eric will be put to the ultimate knowledge test on a weekly basis starting with "Who Wants to be a Millionaire?"

attributes.title: Which Hole Is the Right Hole?! // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: It's time for the boys to get together for a game of golf! Gavin, Andrew, and Nick compete against each other to who see who the best golfer is! Well, let's see if they can actually hit the ball into the hole first.

attributes.title: Winner Picks Our Meal For the Day! // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: We are back with another Golf With Your Friends video! Geoff decides to join this friendly competition... Which may or may not actually make this situation a little more chaotic.

attributes.title: Will ANYONE Become a Millionaire?? // March Mental Madness Part 2
attributes.description: Every Wednesday in the month of March, we'll be releasing an episode of March Mental Madness.  With host Andrew, contestants Graysie and Eric take their turn in "Who Wants to be a Millionaire?" to find out who will be going home and who will be continuing on!

attributes.title: Beating the Absolute Sh*t Out of Each Other // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Your dudes have gathered and are cleaning everyone's clock in Party Animals.

attributes.title: Andrew Is Our Ride-On King // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Andrew takes the wheel on his first SnowRunner Truck Trial while Geoff and Eric "cheer" him on.

attributes.title: The Pursuit of Trivia Greatness // March Mental Madness Part 3
attributes.description: Entering the second round of March Mental Madness, 4 contestants remain and they enter the Trivial Pursuit gauntlet to see which players journey ends here!

attributes.title: Pulling Off the Biggest Heist We Can // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Andrew, Gavin, Eric, and Nick are squading up to play some Payday 3 and rob banks all while being sneaky. Nothing will go wrong, right?

attributes.title: Off To War With the Lads // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: We're strapping on some armor and trotting off to battle in Chivalry 2.

attributes.title: What is Monkey? // March Mental Madness Part 4
attributes.description: With just three contestants remaining, Andrew takes the challengers to Jeopardy!  Who will come out on top?  Who will go home empty handed? And most importantly, What is Monkey?

attributes.title: Scrabble: The Movie // March Mental Madness The Finale
attributes.description: It comes down to this.  Scrabble.  Geoff.  Gavin.  Who will emerge victorious?  And who will be sent home dumber than when this all started?

attributes.title: This GOLF Game’s Got TRUCKS in It! // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Nick ""demands"" everyone play his ""favorite"" game. But to be fair, it's got trucks!

attributes.title: Impromptu Weekend Truck Trials // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description:
Watch part 1 here: https://roosterteeth.com/watch/lets-play-2024-andrew-is-our-ride-on-king-regulation-gameplay
Andrew has got it LOCKED in and he's on the hunt for 3 cars on a map. Only thing is he doesn't know where they are at and he can't use his map. Let's hope his sense of direction is top tier.

attributes.title: Teamwork is ESSENTIAL in Moving Out 2 (#1) // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Whenever you need to hire some movers, these are the guys for the job. Trust me, just let them handle it and  everything will go nice and smooth...

attributes.title: We Can't Get Enough of Turbo Golf Racer // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Turbo Golf Racing is back. Are we addicted to it? Don't worry about that. We just want to win and be really good at this.

attributes.title: Another Day, Another Truck Trials Attempt  // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Andrew has RELOCKED it in and he's here to finish what he's started. Getting those trucks back to the starting spot with no map. Can he do it with Geoff's moral support?

attributes.title: FARM IS NOT MOVING // Regulation Gameplay Pt.2
attributes.description: Back with more Moving Out 2, the Regulation Movers take their talents to the farm to help manage the animals causing havoc as best as they can!

attributes.title: Golf Is For THE BOYS // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: It's time for another Dinner Bet in Golf With Your Friends! This time Eric has joined the battle against Geoff, Nick, and Andrew and man oh man, the competition is ON.

attributes.title: The Iciest Truck Trial Yet // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Truck Trials are back and this time we're trading in the mud for some snow. That's GOT to mean things will be a little easier, right?

attributes.title: EFFICIENTLY INEFFICIENT MOVING // Regulation Gameplay Pt.3
attributes.description: The moving crew is back again and moving out faster than ever before!  They really are moving!  Wow!

attributes.title: Going for WORLD'S FIRST on this Achievement // Regulation Gameplay
attributes.description: Andrew is attempting to be the very first person to unlock an achievement in Expeditions: A MudRunner Game while traversing the bumpy, crazy, wild terrain.
